{"tid":1446973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一解決有鬼嘅方法！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:55.000Z","uid":209678,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da520c058d43c0fe797dac6ab28f17c91dbb7815","tid":1446973,"uid":209678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"勿走散 勿<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐慌</span> 勿戀戰 <br />\n<br />\n保持大隊隊形「齊上齊落」！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係集中返統一戰線一地點，港島區真係要有黃大仙手足既心理先得。<br />\n地型已經不利，心理上嘅恐慌係主要，一驚就散，前線冇後援就會俾人捉"},{"pid":"4ca406e57bdb3660579c815494a3e09fb382ea1a","tid":1446973,"uid":209678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"仲有今次你哋認到嘅特徵，一招改頭換面就得<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為依件事周街查人捉鬼，咁就中咗佢圈套，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己人分化自己人！"},{"pid":"f4a28176513f7dc17cc076c347db6a1f487bbca0","tid":1446973,"uid":259622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/z57whys0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fz57whys0&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=73af4716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/z57whys0</a><br />\n狗扮示威者射催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edfb2d303395d181dd457e5443f4b227b1885a4","tid":1446973,"uid":209678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23aae04746d34712ab2977922a12c352fad06a1a","tid":1446973,"uid":9256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"建議各位前線手足自己組成五個人或以上一個小隊先行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c8f20001ed206dd639b7904434d617eb57302c3","tid":1446973,"uid":38030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"邊個死守邊個係鬼"},{"pid":"0b9a4bafd13481decc717